Description_lang: Imperator Mar'gok summons an Arcane mine that persists for 1 minute.If triggered, Destructive Resonance inflicts $156673s2 Arcane damage to all players. In addition, this effect inflicts $156673s1 Arcane damage to the player that triggered it, increasing their Arcane damage taken by $159200s1% for $159200d and stunning them for $174106d whenever they take Arcane damage.
